    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several popular rumors speak of a hidden treasure somewhere in the home of Tom Barkley, an American archaeologist who moved to Germany. You are looking for the treasure in his house, and after obtaining important information and details about it, you decide to try to recover it.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Hidden Room - Pyramid</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Hidden Room - Pyramid is now out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to explore the depths of the Pyramid and solve the riddles and mysteries that await you along the way. Each step will bring you closer to the truth hidden behind the ancient secrets of this monumental structure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play now and be transported on a journey that will change you forever. The Pyramid waits, ready to reveal its secrets only to those who prove themselves brave enough to face the unknown.</p>",
